Title: Reset Password
英文:
Greetings!

Recently a request was submitted to reset your password. Please visit the URL below to complete the process:
{{.}}

If you did not request this, please ignore this email. It will expire and become useless in 1 hour. If you encounter any issues, please contact us via email (info@chillyroom.com).

Thanks，
ChillyRoom
简体中文:
你好，

我们收到你的账号密码重置请求。请点击以下链接重置密码：
{{.}}

若非本人操作，请忽略此邮件，链接将在1小时候失效。若有其他问题，请联系我们的客服QQ：1597374718。

感谢支持！
凉屋游戏

感謝支持！

{{.}}

{{.}}
